Detailed Description

Internal message class, used to notify a certain operation service of an incoming PanelPassThroughIndication or RawFrameIndication. If this message is received, dependent on the stack message argument, either OnPanelPassThrough or OnRawFrame in the corresponding BtAvrcpOperationService is called.
